<template>
  <select>
    <option v-for="item in data" :key="item.DepartmentId">{{item.DepartmentName}}</option>
  </select>
</template>
<script>
import axios from 'axios'
export default {
  data:{
    data: []
  },
  created(){
    axios.get("https://localhost:7070/api/v1/Departments")
    .then(res => {
      console.log(res)
    })
    .catch(err => {
      console.error(err); 
    })
  }
}
</script>

</style>
